{"id":258,"ayahs":[{"number":19,"arabic":"أَلَمْ تَرَ أَنَّ ٱللَّهَ خَلَقَ ٱلسَّمَٰوَٰتِ وَٱلْأَرْضَ بِٱلْحَقِّ ۚ إِن يَشَأْ يُذْهِبْكُمْ وَيَأْتِ بِخَلْقٍۢ جَدِيدٍۢ","translation":"ART THOU NOT aware that God has created the heavens and the earth in accordance with [an inner] truth? He can, if He so wills, do away with you and bring forth a new mankind [in your stead]:","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1769.mp3","surahId":14,"words":[{"id":22169,"position":1,"arabic":"أَلَمْ","translation":"নি কি","audioUrl":"wbw/014_019_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":22170,"position":2,"arabic":"تَرَ","translation":"তুমি দেখো","audioUrl":"wbw/014_019_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":22171,"position":3,"arabic":"أَنَّ","translation":"যে","audioUrl":"wbw/014_019_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":22172,"position":4,"arabic":"ٱللَّهَ","translation":"আল্লাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/014_019_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":22173,"position":5,"arabic":"خَلَقَ","translation":"সৃষ্টি করেছেন","audioUrl":"wbw/014_019_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":22174,"position":6,"arabic":"ٱلسَّمَـٰوَٰتِ","translation":"আকাশমন্ডলী","audioUrl":"wbw/014_019_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":22175,"position":7,"arabic":"وَٱلْأَرْضَ","translation":"ও পৃথিবী","audioUrl":"wbw/014_019_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":22176,"position":8,"arabic":"بِٱلْحَقِّ ۚ","translation":"সাথে যথার্থতার","audioUrl":"wbw/014_019_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":22178,"position":9,"arabic":"إِن","translation":"যদি","audioUrl":"wbw/014_019_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":22179,"position":10,"arabic":"يَشَأْ","translation":"তিনি ইচ্ছে করেন","audioUrl":"wbw/014_019_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":22180,"position":11,"arabic":"يُذْهِبْكُمْ","translation":"তোমাদের নিয়ে যাবেন","audioUrl":"wbw/014_019_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":22181,"position":12,"arabic":"وَيَأْتِ","translation":"ও আসবেন","audioUrl":"wbw/014_019_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":22182,"position":13,"arabic":"بِخَلْقٍۢ","translation":"নিয়ে সৃষ্টি","audioUrl":"wbw/014_019_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":22183,"position":14,"arabic":"جَدِيدٍۢ","translation":"নয়া","audioUrl":"wbw/014_019_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":22184,"position":15,"arabic":"١٩","translation":"(১৯)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":20,"arabic":"وَمَا ذَٰلِكَ عَلَى ٱللَّهِ بِعَزِيزٍۢ","translation":"nor is this difficult for God.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1770.mp3","surahId":14,"words":[{"id":23222,"position":1,"arabic":"وَمَا","translation":"এবং নয়","audioUrl":"wbw/014_020_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23223,"position":2,"arabic":"ذَٰلِكَ","translation":"এটা","audioUrl":"wbw/014_020_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23224,"position":3,"arabic":"عَلَى","translation":"উপর","audioUrl":"wbw/014_020_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23225,"position":4,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ","translation":"আল্লাহর","audioUrl":"wbw/014_020_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23226,"position":5,"arabic":"بِعَزِيزٍۢ","translation":"কঠিন","audioUrl":"wbw/014_020_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":23227,"position":6,"arabic":"٢٠","translation":"(২০)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":21,"arabic":"وَبَرَزُوا۟ لِلَّهِ جَمِيعًۭا فَقَالَ ٱلضُّعَفَٰٓؤُا۟ لِلَّذِينَ ٱسْتَكْبَرُوٓا۟ إِنَّا كُنَّا لَكُمْ تَبَعًۭا فَهَلْ أَنتُم مُّغْنُونَ عَنَّا مِنْ عَذَابِ ٱللَّهِ مِن شَىْءٍۢ ۚ قَالُوا۟ لَوْ هَدَىٰنَا ٱللَّهُ لَهَدَيْنَٰكُمْ ۖ سَوَآءٌ عَلَيْنَآ أَجَزِعْنَآ أَمْ صَبَرْنَا مَا لَنَا مِن مَّحِيصٍۢ","translation":"And all [mankind] will appear before God [on the Day of Judgment]; and then the weak will say unto those who had gloried in their arrogance: \"Behold, We were but your followers: can you, then, relieve us of something of God's chastisement?\" [And the others] will answer: \"If God would but show us the way [to salvation], we would indeed guide you [towards it]. It is [now] all one, as far as we are concerned, whether we grieve impatiently or endure [our lot] with patience: there is no escape for us!\"","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1771.mp3","surahId":14,"words":[{"id":24232,"position":1,"arabic":"وَبَرَزُوا۟","translation":"এবং তারা উপস্থিত হবে (উন্মোচিত হবে)","audioUrl":"wbw/014_021_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24233,"position":2,"arabic":"لِلَّهِ","translation":"আল্লাহর কাছে","audioUrl":"wbw/014_021_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24234,"position":3,"arabic":"جَمِيعًۭا","translation":"সকলে","audioUrl":"wbw/014_021_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24235,"position":4,"arabic":"فَقَالَ","translation":"অতঃপর বলবে","audioUrl":"wbw/014_021_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24236,"position":5,"arabic":"ٱلضُّعَفَـٰٓؤُا۟","translation":"দুর্বলেরা","audioUrl":"wbw/014_021_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24237,"position":6,"arabic":"لِلَّذِينَ","translation":"তাদেরকে যারা","audioUrl":"wbw/014_021_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24238,"position":7,"arabic":"ٱسْتَكْبَرُوٓا۟","translation":"অহংকার করতো","audioUrl":"wbw/014_021_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24239,"position":8,"arabic":"إِنَّا","translation":"\"আমরা নিশ্চয়ই","audioUrl":"wbw/014_021_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24240,"position":9,"arabic":"كُنَّا","translation":"ছিলাম","audioUrl":"wbw/014_021_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24241,"position":10,"arabic":"لَكُمْ","translation":"তোমাদের জন্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/014_021_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24242,"position":11,"arabic":"تَبَعًۭا","translation":"অধীন","audioUrl":"wbw/014_021_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24243,"position":12,"arabic":"فَهَلْ","translation":"তাহ'লে কি","audioUrl":"wbw/014_021_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24244,"position":13,"arabic":"أَنتُم","translation":"তোমরা","audioUrl":"wbw/014_021_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24245,"position":14,"arabic":"مُّغْنُونَ","translation":"রক্ষাকারী হবে (বাঁচাতে)","audioUrl":"wbw/014_021_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24246,"position":15,"arabic":"عَنَّا","translation":"আমাদেরকে","audioUrl":"wbw/014_021_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24247,"position":16,"arabic":"مِنْ","translation":"থেকে","audioUrl":"wbw/014_021_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24248,"position":17,"arabic":"عَذَابِ","translation":"শাস্তি","audioUrl":"wbw/014_021_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24249,"position":18,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ","translation":"আল্লাহর","audioUrl":"wbw/014_021_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24250,"position":19,"arabic":"مِن","translation":"কোনো\"","audioUrl":"wbw/014_021_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24251,"position":20,"arabic":"شَىْءٍۢ ۚ","translation":"কিছু\"","audioUrl":"wbw/014_021_020.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24253,"position":21,"arabic":"قَالُوا۟","translation":"তারা বলবে","audioUrl":"wbw/014_021_022.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24254,"position":22,"arabic":"لَوْ","translation":"\"যদি","audioUrl":"wbw/014_021_023.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24255,"position":23,"arabic":"هَدَىٰنَا","translation":"আমাদের সৎ পথ দেখাতেন","audioUrl":"wbw/014_021_024.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24256,"position":24,"arabic":"ٱللَّهُ","translation":"আল্লাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/014_021_025.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24257,"position":25,"arabic":"لَهَدَيْنَـٰكُمْ ۖ","translation":"অবশ্যই তোমাদের আমরা পথ দেখাতাম","audioUrl":"wbw/014_021_026.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24259,"position":26,"arabic":"سَوَآءٌ","translation":"সমান","audioUrl":"wbw/014_021_028.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24260,"position":27,"arabic":"عَلَيْنَآ","translation":"আমাদের জন্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/014_021_029.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24261,"position":28,"arabic":"أَجَزِعْنَآ","translation":"আমরা ধৈর্য্যচ্যুত হই","audioUrl":"wbw/014_021_030.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24262,"position":29,"arabic":"أَمْ","translation":"বা","audioUrl":"wbw/014_021_031.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24263,"position":30,"arabic":"صَبَرْنَا","translation":"আমরা ধৈর্য্য ধরি","audioUrl":"wbw/014_021_032.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24264,"position":31,"arabic":"مَا","translation":"নেই","audioUrl":"wbw/014_021_033.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24265,"position":32,"arabic":"لَنَا","translation":"আমাদের জন্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/014_021_034.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24266,"position":33,"arabic":"مِن","translation":"কোনো","audioUrl":"wbw/014_021_035.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24267,"position":34,"arabic":"مَّحِيصٍۢ","translation":"পালানোর জায়গা\"","audioUrl":"wbw/014_021_036.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":24268,"position":35,"arabic":"٢١","translation":"(২১)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":22,"arabic":"وَقَالَ ٱلشَّيْطَٰنُ لَمَّا قُضِىَ ٱلْأَمْرُ إِنَّ ٱللَّهَ وَعَدَكُمْ وَعْدَ ٱلْحَقِّ وَوَعَدتُّكُمْ فَأَخْلَفْتُكُمْ ۖ وَمَا كَانَ لِىَ عَلَيْكُم مِّن سُلْطَٰنٍ إِلَّآ أَن دَعَوْتُكُمْ فَٱسْتَجَبْتُمْ لِى ۖ فَلَا تَلُومُونِى وَلُومُوٓا۟ أَنفُسَكُم ۖ مَّآ أَنَا۠ بِمُصْرِخِكُمْ وَمَآ أَنتُم بِمُصْرِخِىَّ ۖ إِنِّى كَفَرْتُ بِمَآ أَشْرَكْتُمُونِ مِن قَبْلُ ۗ إِنَّ ٱلظَّٰلِمِينَ لَهُمْ عَذَابٌ أَلِيمٌۭ","translation":"And when everything will have been decided, Satan will say: \"Behold, God promised you something that was bound to come true! I, too, held out [all manner of] promises to you -but I deceived you. Yet I had no power at all over you: I but called you-and you responded unto me. Hence, blame not me, but blame yourselves. It is not for me to respond to your cries, nor for you to respond to mine: for, behold, I have [always] refused to admit that there was any truth in your erstwhile belief that I had a share in God's divinity.\" Verily, for all evildoers there is grievous suffering in store.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1772.mp3","surahId":14,"words":[{"id":25211,"position":1,"arabic":"وَقَالَ","translation":"এবং বলবে","audioUrl":"wbw/014_022_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":25212,"position":2,"arabic":